rtices, specified as ","type":"text"},{"code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" instances, and the edges that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNPolygon","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic"}}}